OL,3,CTemperatures could reach mid-20s by
OL,4,CBank Holiday weekend, Met Office says
OL,6,FTemperatures could reach the mid-20s
OL,7,Fjust in time for the late May bank
OL,8,Fholiday weekend, according to
OL,9,Fforecasters.
OL,11,FIt will be a welcome change to Britons
OL,12,Fwho faced blustery showers and chilly
OL,13,Fbreezes on Wednesday, when
OL,14,Ftemperatures were "widely below
OL,15,Faverage", according to the Met Office.
OL,17,FWith a brisk north-westerly wind
OL,18,Fblowing through much of the country,
OL,19,Fthe forecaster said it felt like
OL,20,Ftemperatures had dropped to single
OL,21,Ffigures in some areas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
