OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778746011
OL,3,CTemperatures could reach mid-20s by
OL,4,CBank Holiday weekend, Met Office says
OL,6,FBut early forecasts suggest this may
OL,7,Fchange by the May 24 Bank Holiday.
OL,9,FMet Office meteorologist Annie
OL,10,FShuttleworth, said: "By the end of
OL,11,Fnext week and the start of the bank
OL,12,Fholiday weekend, temperatures could be
OL,13,Fabove average, possibly in the low 20s
OL,14,Ffor some areas."
OL,16,FThe "warming trend" looks likely to
OL,17,Fprogress as there is "going to be a
OL,18,Fmove from low pressure to high
OL,19,Fpressure dominating" the weather.
OL,26,@rD@UOUvD@PO]xD@EOUxD@SO]yD@VOU{D@TO]
