OL,3,CTemperatures could reach mid-20s by
OL,4,CBank Holiday weekend, Met Office says
OL,6,FBut Ms Shuttleworth warned "as that is
OL,7,F10 days away, there are some details
OL,8,Fto work out".
OL,10,FShe said there could be high pressure
OL,11,Fin the east to start the week which
OL,12,Fthen becomes more centred across the
OL,13,FUK during the bank holiday weekend.
OL,15,F"Whatever position that high pressure
OL,16,Fbrings ` all of them bring less cloud,
OL,17,Fa little bit more sunshine, and
OL,18,Flighter winds, which means
OL,19,Ftemperatures will be on the rise
OL,20,Fthrough next week."
OL,26,@nD@\OUpD@LO]wD@AOU|D@SO]
