OL,3,CTemperatures could reach mid-20s by
OL,4,CBank Holiday weekend, Met Office says
OL,6,FTemperatures may slowly start to rise
OL,7,Ffrom the start of next week.
OL,9,FMs Shuttleworth said: "From Thursday
OL,10,Fonwards, temperatures could rise above
OL,11,Faverage, approaching 20 degrees for
OL,12,Fsome across southern areas.
OL,14,F"We could be closer to the mid 20s,
OL,15,Fpossibly, for some areas, in the South
OL,16,FEast, by the bank holiday weekend."
OL,18,FThere is "a little bit of uncertainty"
OL,19,Fabout where the higher temperatures
OL,20,Fwill be, she added.
OL,26,@qD@WOUvD@AOUxD@cO]zD@JOUzD@fO]
