OL,3,CTemperatures could reach mid-20s by
OL,4,CBank Holiday weekend, Met Office says
OL,6,FIn its long range forecast covering
OL,7,FMay 18-27, the Met Office suggests
OL,8,Fthat changeable conditions, including
OL,9,Frain showers, look set to "dominate at
OL,10,Ffirst".
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,F"As this period progresses, high
OL,18,Fpressure is likely to begin to build
OL,19,Ffrom the south bringing more settled
OL,20,Fweather, although with occasional
OL,21,Fshowers," the forecaster adds.
OL,26,@qD@[OUrD@FO]yD@AOU}D@IO]
