OL,3,CTemperatures could reach mid-20s by
OL,4,CBank Holiday weekend, Met Office says
OL,6,F"Temperatures near-normal to begin,
OL,7,Fbut tending to recover as the period
OL,8,Fprogresses, perhaps becoming rather
OL,9,Fwarm by the end of the period,
OL,10,Fespecially in the south.
OL,12,F"Winds will be stronger during the
OL,13,Ffirst part of the period, generally
OL,14,Ffrom a south-westerly direction,
OL,15,Fbefore becoming lighter in line with
OL,16,Fthe more settled conditions."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@]O]
